  ('civil-engineer-moex-00018', 'civil-engineer', 'civil-engineer-moex-110-1ca4f053', 'sub-civil-engineer-01', NULL, 'essay', '某工程基地依照設計圖面要進行土方開挖量為實方 9800 M3，業主給予
