  ('civil-engineer-moex-00019', 'civil-engineer', 'civil-engineer-moex-110-1ca4f053', 'sub-civil-engineer-01', NULL, 'essay', '某公共工程已進行 50 組混凝土強度試驗，並據以計算混凝土強度之平
