  ('civil-engineer-moex-00025', 'civil-engineer', 'civil-engineer-moex-107-1ca4f053', 'sub-civil-engineer-01', NULL, 'essay', '某公共工程的預算為 10 億元，假設其中鋼筋工項的預算單價為每噸
