  ('civil-engineer-moex-00026', 'civil-engineer', 'civil-engineer-moex-107-1ca4f053', 'sub-civil-engineer-01', NULL, 'essay', '某公共工程有關物價調整處理之契約條款，為以下規定：「施作當月營
